Frank HAYS, Jr., Divisional Director of Immigration and Naturalization, Omaha, Nebraska, Appellant, v. Stilianos G. PAN-TAZES or Steve Pantages. No. 10871. Circuit Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. March 6, 1937.

For opinion below, see 15 F.Supp. 1053.

E. G. Dunn, U. S. Attorney, of Mason Sity, Iowa, for appellant. J. E. Williams, of Mason City, Iowa, for appellee. PER CURIAM.

Appeal docketed and dismissed without costs to either party in this court, on motion of appellant and consent of appellee.
